= module GLib::UCS4

== Module Functions

--- GLib::UCS4.to_utf16(ucs4)
     Convert a string from UCS-4 to UTF-16. If the
     conversion is not successful, it causes
     GLib::ConvertError.

     * ucs4: a UCS-4 encoded String
     * Returns: a UTF-16 encoded String

--- GLib::UCS4.to_utf8(ucs4)
     Convert a string from UCS-4 to UTF-8. If the
     conversion is not successful, it causes
     GLib::ConvertError.

     * ucs4: a UCS-4 encoded String
     * Returns: a UTF-8 encoded String

